{"tid":1555392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位於星期一至五定為文宣日。","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T02:43:35.000Z","uid":45486,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b71cc7e27e6260b00f9afdcc711092c2de1bdc","tid":1555392,"uid":45486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:39:40.000Z","msg":"首先，最近文宣力度實在太嚴重不足。<br />\n導致到好多行動同活動都容易失焦。<br />\n運動進入了一個樽頸位已成事實，我想希望大家抱着呢個熱情。<br />\n<br />\n運動發展至今唔係冇嘢做㗎大家，<br />\n<br />\n請大家集中文宣，一張張文宣派又好貼又好<br />\n<br />\n另外文宣其實唔應該集中於連儂牆，<br />\n能夠貼到文宣嘅地方我哋應該都要貼，巴士站，電梯大堂，紅綠燈位等等。<br />\n希望大家每人每日都貼三張文宣，非常之和理非，好過你圍狗屋。<br />\n<br />\n有10000人貼每日3張，已有3萬張<br />\n一星期貼5日已有15萬，撕紙狗都撕到手軟。"},{"pid":"47819bbbf521c892fac4ce34812d391f2aedf398","tid":1555392,"uid":45486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:41:09.000Z","msg":"除左連登，地區都要做架各位。"},{"pid":"4198455f3ef20d6f80a0c13e5298ef34d3862e5c","tid":1555392,"uid":263221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"係，每人貼幾張"},{"pid":"f28810f2806e929d477357de2417cd9ef36f46e2","tid":1555392,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:45:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c66b0cd755b269065e39fb892102b9083f7976d7","tid":1555392,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"岩聽"},{"pid":"5be6519d99c9de874a278f2323ff3dce93f36aae","tid":1555392,"uid":288537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"130086a089722e8dc196528699bc091b1cc4ff57","tid":1555392,"uid":92277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗唔係無人撐，係因為無人知</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文宣我認為係難道最低而又可以幫到成個運動既一件事。<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實整圖既巴打唔介意人地偷圖，只會怪人睇完唔forward! </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔識整圖既大家，我有三樣野希望大家幫幫手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.分享去 Facebook IG Whatsapp Gp </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n難聽講句，IG story輕鬆都百幾二百人睇啦！連登接觸面唔係唔廣，但可以再廣啲，而且留得係到既已經係跟得好貼既人。希望大家見到靚既文宣，由其<span style=\"color: red;\">行動post</span>，幫一幫手做多步，repost 埋上ig, facebook, WhatsApp 之類既社交評台。一人拉多一個人去遊行就已經多好多。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<br />\n200萬人有幾多個真係睇連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542401\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 貼連儂牆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然依家科技發達，但仲有好多人無辦法係果到收到信息。平時我等車都會望到好多叔叔望下牆。其實佢真係好吸睛，都係直接文宣既好地方!<br />\n<br />\n**建議組隊進行，放工放學咪貼兩張。<br />\n**如要去廠印刷，落單要開新Account <br />\n<br />\n原post:<br />\n老母一句屌醒左我，駁唔到。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546699\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣組入！印刷都會出事！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dPQbDT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dPQbDT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. Airdrop 比全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n0成本，直接塞信息比人，<span style=\"color: red;\">行動post 優先</span>。平時搭車，行街得閒無野做咪用下！<br />\n<br />\n原post: <br />\n<br />\nIPhone有個咁好用既功能點解要浪費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551471\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551471</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ld9NuBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLd9NuBN.jpg&h=2115e932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzQQsos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzQQsos.jpg&h=35463d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUOniu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUOniu8.jpg&h=ad130f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！光復之日，煲底相聚💛</span>"},{"pid":"e6b28751d3dee7546fcc48dbd54dc87683a87d57","tid":1555392,"uid":45486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:53:08.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"6000dee385cb355d67739fc2f7b3c3c31200dd2b","tid":1555392,"uid":13053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"有冇文宣行動gp？<br />\ntg等等<br />\n可以gp哂所有手足一齊貼"},{"pid":"6a27a671f0521f3760fa60d6b27991a282ad9923","tid":1555392,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"支持！即印文宣！"},{"pid":"68b5d949c5a200c24dde4beea108bd89fe1b4c06","tid":1555392,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"345b6162b497010e4b449028474b2daa01c9ed6d","tid":1555392,"uid":287410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47c29ed00d9b8f9dcae951868c23821c1726dafd","tid":1555392,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eb658e8800062b1e65e0d218187310b8f6f477f","tid":1555392,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7D4ef9Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7D4ef9Z.png&h=372d733e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N20XYoj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN20XYoj.png&h=94801332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月14同9月15個文宣請補上"},{"pid":"eddcbaabedf6361f1f2a59347654181e6527a902","tid":1555392,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64c9311b932512d8ef28038343771b83441e1629","tid":1555392,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"[討論]HK Independence/ Return t